text: Alfonso Barracco (Crotone, March 17, 1810 – Naples, January 15, 1890) was an Italian politician. He served in the Chamber of Deputies of the Kingdom of Sardinia. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1810 births Category:1890 deaths Category:19th-century Italian politicians Category:Members of the Senate of the Kingdom of Sardinia
